From: ASUS ProArt PX13 debug <snd-repair@local>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] ASoC: tas2783: wait for async firmware in hw_params

Firmware is loaded asynchronously after probe. hw_params() can run
before tas2783_fw_ready() completes, causing a spurious "playback
without fw download" error. Wait on the existing fw_wait queue with
the same timeout used elsewhere before rejecting playback.

Signed-off-by: ASUS ProArt PX13 debug <snd-repair@local>
---
 sound/soc/codecs/tas2783-sdw.c | 7 ++++++++
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+)

diff --git a/sound/soc/codecs/tas2783-sdw.c b/sound/soc/codecs/tas2783-sdw.c
--- a/sound/soc/codecs/tas2783-sdw.c
+++ b/sound/soc/codecs/tas2783-sdw.c
@@ -903,6 +903,13 @@
 	struct sdw_slave *sdw_peripheral = tas_dev->sdw_peripheral;
 	s32 ret, retry = 3;
 
+	if (!tas_dev->fw_dl_success && !tas_dev->fw_dl_task_done) {
+		ret = wait_event_timeout(tas_dev->fw_wait, tas_dev->fw_dl_task_done,
+					 msecs_to_jiffies(TIMEOUT_FW_DL_MS));
+		if (!ret)
+			dev_err(tas_dev->dev, "fw download wait timeout in hw_params");
+	}
+
 	if (!tas_dev->fw_dl_success) {
 		dev_err(tas_dev->dev, "error playback without fw download");
 		return -EINVAL;
